,"aggregated":"/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent//AGENT.md\n/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent//tools/validate_declaration.py\n/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent//tools/download_receipt.py\n/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent//tools/config.json\n/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent//tools/init_declaration.py\n/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent//tools/query_policy_kb.py\n/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent//tools/__pycache__/login.cpython-314.pyc\n/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent//tools/__pycache__/submit_declaration.cpython-314.pyc\n/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent//tools/__pycache__/shared.cpython-314.pyc\n/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent//tools/__pycache__/fetch_tax_list.cpython-314.pyc\n/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent//tools/__pycache__/init_declaration.cpython-314.pyc\n/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent//tools/__pycache__/download_receipt.cpython-314.pyc\n/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent//tools/state_machine.py\n/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent//tools/parse_pdf.py\n/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent//tools/shared.py\n/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent//tools/submit_declaration.py\n/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent//tools/calculate_tax.py\n/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent//tools/fetch_tax_list.py\n/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent//tools/login.py\n/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent//tools/check_submit_result.py","cwd":"/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/workspace-qxy-declare"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773821816659}}
{"type":"message","id":"b3b5bcff","parentId":"820c6fef","timestamp":"2026-03-18T08:16:59.775Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"找到了完整的工具集。让我读取AGENT.md（核心流程说明）和状态机。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_fcca72e49ea64ce0b202cbbf","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent/AGENT.md"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_01f39714efdd4802a118ae20","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent/tools/state_machine.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":1923,"output":76,"cacheRead":18474,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20473,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773821816662}}
{"type":"message","id":"08c9d9df","parentId":"b3b5bcff","timestamp":"2026-03-18T08:16:59.789Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_fcca72e49ea64ce0b202cbbf","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# qxy-declare — 纳税申报 Agent\n\n你是纳税申报执行 Agent。你通过**状态机**驱动整个申报流程，在需要\"理解\"和\"判断\"的环节使用 LLM 推理，其余环节调用确定性脚本/API 执行。\n\n---\n\n## 核心原则\n\n1. **状态机驱动**：每个企业的每次申报是一个状态机实例，严格按状态转移执行\n2. **最小 LLM 使用**：只在需要语义理解、模糊判断、异常决策时使用你的推理能力\n3. **确定性优先**：税费计算、数据校验、API 调用等必须使用脚本，绝不用 LLM 推理\n4. **可恢复**：任何状态失败都可以从当前状态重试，不需要从头开始\n\n---\n\n## 状态机定义\n\n```\nINIT → FETCH_LIST → CHECK_REQUIRED → DATA_INIT → WAIT_UPLOAD → PARSE_EXCEL\n     → CONFIRM_INFO → TAX_CALC → VALIDATE → SUBMIT → CHECK_RESULT → DOWNLOAD → DONE\n```\n\n每个状态的详细说明：\n\n### S01: INIT（初始化）\n- **类型**: 脚本\n- **动作**: 接收企业信息，创建申报任务实例，记录 task_id\n- **转移**: → FETCH_LIST\n\n### S02: FETCH_LIST（获取申报清单）\n- **类型**: 脚本 (API)\n- **动作**: 调用税费清单接口，获取本月应申报税种\n- **失败处理**: 重试 3 次，间隔递增。3 次失败 → 状态置为 FAILED，通知上游\n- **转移**: 成功 → CHECK_REQUIRED\n\n### S03: CHECK_REQUIRED（判断是否需要申报）\n- **类型**: 脚本\n- **动作**: 根据清单数据判断本月是否有需申报税种\n- **转移**:\n  - 无需申报 → DONE（通知用户\"本月无需申报\"）\n  - 需要申报 → DATA_INIT\n\n### S04: DATA_INIT（申报表数据初始化）\n- **类型**: 脚本 (API)\n- **动作**: 调用初始化接口，获取各税种申报表预填数据\n- **失败处理**:\n  - 税务局系统不稳定 → 等待后重试\n  - 数据异常 → ⚠️ **LLM 介入**：分析错误信息，决定重试策略或通知用户\n- **转移**: 成功 → WAIT_UPLOAD\n\n### S05: WAIT_UPLOAD（等待用户上传）\n- **类型**: 等待 (人机交互)\n- **动作**: 通知用户上传 Excel 文件\n- **超时**: 可配置超时时间，超时后提醒用户\n- **转移**: 收到文件 → PARSE_EXCEL\n\n### S06: PARSE_EXCEL（解析 Excel）\n- **类型**: ⚠️ **LLM 核心环节**\n- **动作**:\n  1. 读取用户上传的 Excel 文件\n  2. **LLM 推理**：理解 Excel 的结构和语义，识别各列含义\n  3. **LLM 推理**：将用户数据映射到税务局标准字段\n  4. 输出标准化的申报数据 JSON\n- **失败处理**:\n  - 格式无法识别 → 告知用户具体问题，请求重新上传（→ WAIT_UPLOAD）\n  - 数据缺失 → 列出缺失字段，请求补充\n- **转移**: 解析成功 → CONFIRM_INFO\n\n### S07: CONFIRM_INFO（无票收入确认）\n- **类型**: ⚠️ **LLM 环节**（人机交互）\n- **动作**:\n  1. 向用户展示 Excel 解析结果摘要（当前识别的销售额等）\n  2. 询问用户：\"本期是否有无票收入需要补充？\"\n  3. 理解用户回复，执行对应操作：\n\n  **用户说有无票收入**（如\"有，5万\"、\"无票收入50000\"、\"有3万无票\"）：\n  - 从用户回复中提取金额（注意单位，\"5万\"=50000）\n  - 调用: `state_machine.py '{\"action\":\"inject\",\"task_id\":\"...\",\"data_key\":\"no_invoice_income\",\"data_value\":{\"amount\":50000}}'`\n  - 然后: `state_machine.py '{\"action\":\"advance\",\"task_id\":\"...\"}'`\n  - 状态机会自动把金额加到增值税销售额和企业所得税收入里\n\n  **用户说没有**（如\"没有\"、\"无\"、\"不需要\"、\"没有无票收入\"）：\n  - 调用: `state_machine.py '{\"action\":\"inject\",\"task_id\":\"...\",\"data_key\":\"user_confirmations\",\"data_value\":{\"confirmed\":true}}'`\n  - 然后: `state_machine.py '{\"action\":\"advance\",\"task_id\":\"...\"}'`\n  - 直接跳过进入税费计算\n\n- **转移**: → TAX_CALC\n\n### S08: TAX_CALC（税费计提）\n- **类型**: 脚本\n- **动作**:\n  1. 根据标准化数据，按公式计算各税种应缴金额\n  2. 判断是否全零申报\n- **全零判断**: 如果所有税种应缴金额 = 0 → 直接走快速通道提交零申报\n- **转移**:\n  - 全零 → SUBMIT（零申报模式）\n  - 非零 → VALIDATE\n\n### S09: VALIDATE（校验）\n- **类型**: 脚本 + ⚠️ **LLM 辅助**\n- **动作**:\n  1. **脚本**: 执行申报表逻辑校验（勾稽关系、数值范围、必填项）\n  2. **脚本**: 调用预申报接口，获取税务局校验结果\n  3. **LLM（仅在校验失败时）**: 分析校验错误，判断是数据问题还是规则变更，给出修正建议\n- **失败处理**: 校验不通过 → 根据错误类型决定回退到哪个状态\n- **转移**: 校验通过 → SUBMIT\n\n### S10: POLICY_CHECK（优惠政策检查）\n- **类型**: ⚠️ **LLM 环节**\n- **动作**:\n  1. 调取优惠政策知识库\n  2. **LLM 推理**：比对企业数据与最新优惠政策，判断是否适用\n  3. 如适用，自动填写优惠申报信息\n- **注意**: 此步骤在 VALIDATE 之前或与 TAX_CALC 并行执行\n- **转移**: → VALIDATE\n\n### S11: SUBMIT（提交申报）\n- **类型**: 脚本 (API)\n- **动作**: 调用一键申报/批量申报接口\n- **转移**: → CHECK_RESULT\n\n### S12: CHECK_RESULT（检查结果）\n- **类型**: 脚本 + ⚠️ **LLM（失败时）**\n- **动作**:\n  1. **脚本**: 轮询或回调获取申报结果\n  2. 成功 → DOWNLOAD\n  3. 失败 → **LLM 介入**：分析失败原因（税务局拦截、数据错误、系统故障等），决定处理策略：\n     - 可自动修复 → 回退到对应状态重试\n     - 需人工介入 → 挂起，通知用户\n- **转移**: 成功 → DOWNLOAD\n\n### S13: DOWNLOAD（下载回执）\n- **类型**: 脚本\n- **动作**:\n  1. 下载申报 PDF 回执\n  2. OCR / 结构化识别 PDF 内容\n  3. 存档申报数据\n- **转移**: → DONE\n\n### S14: DONE（完成）\n- **类型**: 脚本\n- **动作**: 通知上游（qxy-accounting），发送结果给用户\n\n### FAILED（失败终态）\n- **动作**: 记录失败原因，通知上游，等待人工干预或重新触发\n\n---\n\n## 你的行为规则\n\n### 当你被调用时\n\n1. 先查看当前申报任务的状态（读取状态文件）\n2. 从当前状态继续执行，不要从头开始\n3. 每完成一个状态转移，立即持久化新状态\n\n### 脚本环节（不要用 LLM 推理）\n\n以下操作必须调用对应的 Tool / MCP / 脚本，你只负责传参和处理返回值：\n- `fetch_tax_list` — 获取申报清单\n- `init_declaration` — 初始化申报表\n- `calculate_tax` — 税费计算\n- `validate_declaration` — 申报表校验\n- `submit_declaration` — 提交申报\n- `check_result` — 查询申报结果\n- `download_receipt` — 下载回执 PDF\n- `parse_pdf` — PDF 结构化识别\n\n### LLM 环节（需要你推理）\n\n只在以下场景使用你的推理能力：\n1. **Excel 解析**: 理解用户上传文件的结构，映射到标准字段\n2. **用户交互**: 理解自然语言回复，提取结构化信息\n3. **优惠政策判断**: 结合企业数据和政策知识库做匹配\n4. **异常决策**: 分析错误信息，判断处理策略\n\n### 状态持久化格式\n\n每个任务的状态存储为 JSON：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"task_id\": \"decl_20260301_company123\",\n  \"company_id\": \"company123\",\n  \"company_name\": \"某某公司\",\n  \"period\": \"2026-02\",\n  \"state\": \"PARSE_EXCEL\",\n  \"state_history\": [\n    {\"state\": \"INIT\", \"at\": \"2026-03-01T10:00:00Z\", \"result\": \"ok\"},\n    {\"state\": \"FETCH_LIST\", \"at\": \"2026-03-01T10:00:01Z\", \"result\": \"ok\"},\n    {\"state\": \"CHECK_REQUIRED\", \"at\": \"2026-03-01T10:00:02Z\", \"result\": \"required\"},\n    {\"state\": \"DATA_INIT\", \"at\": \"2026-03-01T10:00:05Z\", \"result\": \"ok\"},\n    {\"state\": \"WAIT_UPLOAD\", \"at\": \"2026-03-01T10:00:06Z\", \"result\": \"file_received\"},\n    {\"state\": \"PARSE_EXCEL\", \"at\": \"2026-03-01T10:01:00Z\", \"result\": \"pending\"}\n  ],\n  \"data\": {\n    \"tax_list\": [...],\n    \"declaration_forms\": {...},\n    \"parsed_excel\": {...},\n    \"user_confirmations\": {...},\n    \"calculated_taxes\": {...},\n    \"submit_result\": null,\n    \"receipt_url\": null\n  },\n  \"retry_count\": 0,\n  \"max_retries\": 3,\n  \"error\": null\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 与上游通信\n\n你通过 agent-to-agent 调用与 `qxy-accounting` 通信：\n- **接收**: 企业信息、申报指令、用户上传的文件\n- **上报**: 状态变更、需要用户交互的消息、最终结果\n\n## 错误处理原则\n\n1. 网络/系统错误 → 自动重试（最多 3 次，指数退避）\n2. 数据错误 → 分析原因，尝试自动修正或请求用户补充\n3. 税务局拦截 → 解读拦截信息，给出具体建议\n4. 未知错误 → 挂起任务，上报给 qxy-accounting，等待人工处理\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773821819784}}
{"type":"message","id":"60242fe0","parentId":"08c9d9df","timestamp":"2026-03-18T08:16:59.806Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_01f39714efdd4802a118ae20","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nstate_machine.py — 申报流程状态机引擎（企享云版）\n\n所有接口走企享云异步模式：发起任务 → 轮询 taskId → 拿结果\n\n用法:\n  python state_machine.py '{\"action\":\"create\", \"company_id\":\"c001\", \"company_name\":\"测试公司\",\n                            \"agg_org_id\":\"12345\", \"period\":\"2026-02\", \"company_type\":\"small_scale\"}'\n  python state_machine.py '{\"action\":\"advance\", \"task_id\":\"decl_202602_c001\"}'\n  python state_machine.py '{\"action\":\"inject\", \"task_id\":\"...\", \"data_key\":\"...\", \"data_value\":{...}}'\n  python state_machine.py '{\"action\":\"status\", \"task_id\":\"...\"}'\n  python state_machine.py '{\"action\":\"list\"}'\n\"\"\"\n\nfrom shared import (\n    create_task, load_state, save_state, transition, fail,\n    list_tasks, output, parse_args, log, now_iso,\n)\n\nfrom login import ensure_logged_in\nfrom fetch_tax_list import fetch_tax_list\nfrom init_declaration import init_declaration\nfrom submit_declaration import submit_standard, submit_simplified, submit_financial_report\nfrom download_receipt import download_receipt\n# from payment import execute_payment  # TODO: not yet implemented\n\n\n# ── 辅助：从 period 提取 year 和 period_num ──────────\ndef _parse_period(period_str: str) -> tuple[int, int]:\n    \"\"\"'2026-02' → (2026, 2)\"\"\"\n    parts = period_str.split(\"-\")\n    return int(parts[0]), int(parts[1])\n\n\n# ── 状态处理器 ────────────────────────────────────────\n\ndef handle_INIT(state: dict) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"初始化：确认登录状态\"\"\"\n    agg_org_id = state[\"agg_org_id\"]\n\n    if not agg_org_id:\n        return {\n            **state,\n            \"_need_llm\": True,\n            \"_llm_context\": {\n                \"situation\": \"missing_agg_org_id\",\n                \"message\": \"缺少企业聚合ID (aggOrgId)，请提供企业信息\",\n            },\n        }\n\n    # 检查登录状态\n    login_result = ensure_logged_in(agg_org_id)\n    if not login_result[\"ok\"]:\n        if login_result.get(\"need_natural_person_login\"):\n            return {\n                **state,\n                \"_need_llm\": True,\n                \"_llm_context\": {\n                    \"situation\": \"need_login\",\n                    \"message\": \"税局登录已失效，需要重新进行自然人登录\",\n                    \"action\": \"请调用 qxy-login 子 agent 完成登录\",\n                },\n            }\n        fail(state, login_result.get(\"error\", \"登录失败\"))\n        return state\n\n    return transition(state, \"FETCH_LIST\", \"logged_in\")\n\n\ndef handle_FETCH_LIST(state: dict) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"获取应申报清册\"\"\"\n    year, period_num = _parse_period(state[\"period\"])\n\n    result = fetch_tax_list(state[\"agg_org_id\"], year, period_num)\n\n    if not result[\"ok\"]:\n        fail(state, result.get(\"error\", \"获取清册失败\"))\n        if state[\"retry_count\"] >= state[\"max_retries\"]:\n            return transition(state, \"FAILED\", \"max_retries_exceeded\")\n        return state\n\n    state[\"data\"][\"tax_list\"] = result\n    save_state(state[\"task_id\"], state)\n    return transition(state, \"CHECK_REQUIRED\", \"ok\")\n\n\ndef handle_CHECK_REQUIRED(state: dict) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"判断是否需要申报\"\"\"\n    tax_list = state[\"data\"].get(\"tax_list\", {})\n\n    if not tax_list.get(\"has_required\"):\n        return {\n            **state,\n            \"_need_llm\": True,\n            \"_llm_context\": {\n                \"situation\": \"no_required\",\n                \"message\": f\"{state['company_name']} 本月无需申报\",\n                \"action\": \"通知用户本月无需申报\",\n            },\n        }\n\n    # 通知用户需要申报的税种\n    required = tax_list.get(\"required_items\", [])\n    return {\n        **state,\n        \"_need_llm\": True,\n        \"_llm_context\": {\n            \"situation\": \"report_required_taxes\",\n            \"required_items\": required,\n            \"required_count\": len(required),\n            \"message\": f\"本月需申报 {len(required)} 个税种，通知用户并开始流程\",\n            \"action\": \"告知用户本月需申报的税种清单，然后 inject data_key='proceed' data_value=true 继续\",\n        },\n    }\n\n\ndef handle_CHECK_REQUIRED_proceed(state: dict) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"用户确认后继续\"\"\"\n    return transition(state, \"DATA_INIT\", \"required\")\n\n\ndef handle_DATA_INIT(state: dict) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"申报表数据初始化\"\"\"\n    year, period_num = _parse_period(state[\"period\"])\n    tax_list = state[\"data\"].get(\"tax_list\", {})\n    required_items = tax_list.get(\"required_items\", [])\n\n    result = init_declaration(state[\"agg_org_id\"], year, period_num, required_items)\n\n    state[\"data\"][\"init_data\"] = result\n    save_state(state[\"task_id\"], state)\n\n    if result.get(\"errors\"):\n        return {\n            **state,\n            \"_need_llm\": True,\n            \"_llm_context\": {\n                \"situation\": \"init_partial_failure\",\n                \"initialized\": result.get(\"results\", []),\n                \"errors\": result.get(\"errors\", []),\n                \"message\": f\"部分税种初始化失败: {len(result['errors'])} 个错误\",\n                \"action\": \"分析错误原因，决定是跳过还是重试\",\n            },\n        }\n\n    return transition(state, \"WAIT_UPLOAD\", \"ok\")\n\n\ndef handle_WAIT_UPLOAD(state: dict) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"等待用户上传 Excel\"\"\"\n    if state[\"data\"].get(\"parsed_excel\"):\n        return transition(state, \"CONFIRM_INFO\", \"already_parsed\")\n\n    return {\n        **state,\n        \"_need_user_input\": True,\n        \"_prompt\": \"请上传本月的申报数据 Excel 文件（仅支持 .xlsx 格式）\",\n        \"_waiting_for\": \"excel_upload\",\n    }\n\n\ndef handle_PARSE_EXCEL(state: dict) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"解析 Excel — LLM 环节\"\"\"\n    return {\n        **state,\n        \"_need_llm\": True,\n        \"_llm_context\": {\n            \"situation\": \"parse_excel\",\n            \"excel_data\": state[\"data\"].get(\"uploaded_excel\"),\n            \"init_data\": state[\"data\"].get(\"init_data\"),\n            \"company_type\": state.get(\"company_type\", \"small_scale\"),\n            \"message\": \"请解析用户上传的 Excel，映射到企享云标准申报报文格式\",\n        },\n    }\n\n\ndef handle_CONFIRM_INFO(state: dict) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"\n    信息确认 — LLM 环节（无票收入）\n\n    流程:\n    1. 状态机暂停，让 Agent 问用户\"是否有无票收入\"\n    2. Agent 理解用户回复后，inject 数据:\n       - 用户说\"有，5万\": inject data_key=\"no_invoice_income\" data_value={\"amount\": 50000}\n       - 用户说\"没有\":    inject data_key=\"user_confirmations\" data_value={\"confirmed\": true}\n    3. 再次 advance 时:\n       - 有无票收入 → 加到 parsed_excel 的 vat.sales_amount 里，然后进入 TAX_CALC\n       - 没有 → 直接进入 TAX_CALC\n    \"\"\"\n    confirmations = state[\"data\"].get(\"user_confirmations\") or {}\n    no_invoice = state[\"data\"].get(\"no_invoice_income\")\n\n    # 情况1: 用户确认没有无票收入 → 直接进入计算\n    if confirmations.get(\"confirmed\"):\n        return transition(state, \"TAX_CALC\", \"confirmed_no_extra_income\")\n\n    # 情况2: 用户提供了无票收入金额 → 加到销售额里，然后进入计算\n    if no_invoice and no_invoice.get(\"amount\", 0) > 0:\n        amount = no_invoice[\"amount\"]\n\n        # 把无票收入加到 parsed_excel 的增值税销售额里\n        parsed = state[\"data\"].get(\"parsed_excel\") or {}\n        vat_data = parsed.get(\"vat\") or {}\n        old_sales = vat_data.get(\"sales_amount\", 0)\n        vat_data[\"sales_amount\"] = old_sales + amount\n        vat_data[\"no_invoice_income\"] = amount  # 记录无票收入明细\n        parsed[\"vat\"] = vat_data\n        state[\"data\"][\"parsed_excel\"] = parsed\n\n        # 同样加到企业所得税的收入里\n        cit_data = parsed.get(\"cit\") or {}\n        old_revenue = cit_data.get(\"revenue\", 0)\n        cit_data[\"revenue\"] = old_revenue + amount\n        cit_data[\"no_invoice_income\"] = amount\n        parsed[\"cit\"] = cit_data\n        state[\"data\"][\"parsed_excel\"] = parsed\n\n        save_state(state[\"task_id\"], state)\n        log.info(f\"[{state['task_id']}] 无票收入 {amount} 已加入销售额 (增值税: {old_sales}→{old_sales + amount})\")\n        return transition(state, \"TAX_CALC\", f\"confirmed_with_no_invoice_{amount}\")\n\n    # 情况3: 还没问过用户 → 暂停，让 Agent 去问\n    parsed = state[\"data\"].get(\"parsed_excel\") or {}\n    vat_data = parsed.get(\"vat\") or {}\n    current_sales = vat_data.get(\"sales_amount\", 0)\n\n    return {\n        **state,\n        \"_need_llm\": True,\n        \"_llm_context\": {\n            \"situation\": \"confirm_no_invoice_income\",\n            \"current_sales\": current_sales,\n            \"parsed_data_summary\": {\n                \"vat_sales\": vat_data.get(\"sales_amount\", 0),\n                \"cit_revenue\": (parsed.get(\"cit\") or {}).get(\"revenue\", 0),\n            },\n            \"message\": (\n                \"请询问用户：本期是否有无票收入需要补充？\\n\"\n                f\"当前已识别的销售额为: ¥{current_sales}\\n\\n\"\n                \"用户回复后请按以下方式处理：\\n\"\n                '- 用户说有无票收入（如\"有，5万\"）→ inject data_key=\"no_invoice_income\" data_value={\"amount\": 50000}\\n'\n                '- 用户说没有 → inject data_key=\"user_confirmations\" data_value={\"confirmed\": true}\\n'\n                \"然后再次 advance 继续流程。\"\n            ),\n        },\n    }\n\n\ndef handle_TAX_CALC(state: dict) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"税费计算（脚本，确定性）\"\"\"\n    from calculate_tax import calculate_tax\n\n    tax_list = state[\"data\"].get(\"tax_list\", {})\n    tax_codes = [item.get(\"yzpzzlDm\", item.get(\"tax_code\", \"\"))\n                 for item in tax_list.get(\"required_items\", [])]\n\n    result = calculate_tax(\n        company_id=state[\"company_id\"],\n        period=state[\"period\"],\n        declaration_data=state[\"data\"].get(\"parsed_excel\", {}),\n        tax_codes=tax_codes,\n        company_type=state.get(\"company_type\", \"small_scale\"),\n    )\n\n    state[\"data\"][\"calculated_taxes\"] = result\n    save_state(state[\"task_id\"], state)\n\n    if result.get(\"is_all_zero\"):\n        return transition(state, \"SUBMIT\", \"all_zero\")\n\n    # 展示计算结果给用户确认\n    return {\n        **state,\n        \"_need_llm\": True,\n        \"_llm_context\": {\n            \"situation\": \"show_tax_calculation\",\n            \"results\": result.get(\"results\", []),\n            \"total_payable\": result.get(\"total_payable\", 0),\n            \"message\": \"向用户展示税费计算结果，确认无误后继续申报\",\n            \"action\": \"确认后 inject data_key='tax_confirmed' data_value=true\",\n        },\n    }\n\n\ndef handle_SUBMIT(state: dict) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"提交申报\"\"\"\n    year, period_num = _parse_period(state[\"period\"])\n    agg_org_id = state[\"agg_org_id\"]\n    is_all_zero = state[\"data\"].get(\"calculated_taxes\", {}).get(\"is_all_zero\", False)\n    company_type = state.get(\"company_type\", \"small_scale\")\n\n    # 全零申报走简易通道\n    if is_all_zero and company_type in (\"small_scale\", \"general\"):\n        result = submit_simplified(agg_org_id, year, period_num, sb_init=True)\n    else:\n        report_data = state[\"data\"].get(\"parsed_excel\", {}).get(\"report_payload\", {})\n        result = submit_standard(agg_org_id, year, period_num, report_data)\n\n    state[\"data\"][\"submit_result\"] = result\n    save_state(state[\"task_id\"], state)\n\n    if not result[\"ok\"]:\n        error_type = result.get(\"error_type\", \"unknown\")\n        error_msg = result.get(\"error\", \"申报失败\")\n\n        # 可重试的系统错误\n        if result.get(\"retryable\"):\n            fail(state, error_msg)\n            if state[\"retry_count\"] < state[\"max_retries\"]:\n                return state\n            return transition(state, \"FAILED\", \"max_retries_exceeded\")\n\n        # 需要 LLM 分析的业务错误\n        return {\n            **state,\n            \"_need_llm\": True,\n            \"_llm_context\": {\n                \"situation\": \"submit_failed\",\n                \"error\": error_msg,\n                \"error_type\": error_type,\n                \"code\": result.get(\"code\"),\n                \"data\": result.get(\"data\"),\n                \"message\": f\"申报失败 [{error_type}]: {error_msg}\",\n                \"action\": \"根据错误类型决定处理策略（参考 API 常见返回异常表）\",\n            },\n        }\n\n    return transition(state, \"DOWNLOAD\", \"submitted\")\n\n\ndef handle_DOWNLOAD(state: dict) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"下载 PDF 回执\"\"\"\n    year, period_num = _parse_period(state[\"period\"])\n    tax_list = state[\"data\"].get(\"tax_list\", {})\n    required = tax_list.get(\"required_items\", [])\n\n    zsxm_list = [\n        {\"yzpzzlDm\": item.get(\"yzpzzlDm\", \"\")}\n        for item in required\n        if item.get(\"yzpzzlDm\")\n    ]\n\n    result = download_receipt(state[\"agg_org_id\"], year, period_num, zsxm_list)\n\n    state[\"data\"][\"receipt_data\"] = result.get(\"structured_data\")\n    state[\"data\"][\"pdf_data\"] = result.get(\"pdf_data\")\n    save_state(state[\"task_id\"], state)\n\n    if not result[\"ok\"]:\n        log.warning(f\"PDF 下载失败: {result.get('error')}，但申报已成功\")\n\n    return transition(state, \"DONE\", \"ok\")\n\n\ndef handle_DONE(state: dict) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"完成\"\"\"\n    taxes = state[\"data\"].get(\"calculated_taxes\", {})\n    return {\n        **state,\n        \"_completed\": True,\n        \"_summary\": {\n            \"task_id\": state[\"task_id\"],\n            \"company_name\": state[\"company_name\"],\n            \"period\": state[\"period\"],\n            \"status\": \"completed\",\n            \"total_payable\": taxes.get(\"total_payable\", 0),\n            \"is_all_zero\": taxes.get(\"is_all_zero\", False),\n            \"has_pdf\": state[\"data\"].get(\"receipt_data\") is not None,\n            \"message\": f\"{state['company_name']} {state['period']} 申报完成\"\n                       + (f\"，应缴税额: ¥{taxes.get('total_payable', 0)}\" if not taxes.get(\"is_all_zero\") else \"（零申报）\"),\n        },\n    }\n\n\ndef handle_FAILED(state: dict) -> dict:\n    \"\"\"失败\"\"\"\n    return {\n        **state,\n        \"_completed\": True,\n        \"_failed\": True,\n        \"_summary\": {\n            \"task_id\": state[\"task_id\"],\n            \"company_name\": state[\"company_name\"],\n            \"period\": state[\"period\"],\n            \"status\": \"failed\",\n            \"error\": state.get(\"error\"),\n            \"last_state\": state[\"state_history\"][-1][\"state\"] if state[\"state_history\"] else \"INIT\",\n            \"message\": f\"{state['company_name']} {state['period']} 申报失败: {state.get('error')}\",\n        },\n    }\n\n\n# ── 状态处理器映射 ────────────────────────────────────\nHANDLERS = {\n    \"INIT\":           handle_INIT,\n    \"FETCH_LIST\":     handle_FETCH_LIST,\n    \"CHECK_REQUIRED\": handle_CHECK_REQUIRED,\n    \"DATA_INIT\":      handle_DATA_INIT,\n    \"WAIT_UPLOAD\":    handle_WAIT_UPLOAD,\n    \"PARSE_EXCEL\":    handle_PARSE_EXCEL,\n    \"CONFIRM_INFO\":   handle_CONFIRM_INFO,\n    \"TAX_CALC\":       handle_TAX_CALC,\n    \"SUBMIT\":         handle_SUBMIT,\n    \"DOWNLOAD\":       handle_DOWNLOAD,\n    \"DONE\":           handle_DONE,\n    \"FAILED\":         handle_FAILED,\n}\n\n\n# ── 主引擎 ────────────────────────────────────────────\n\ndef advance(task_id: str) -> dict:\n    state = load_state(task_id)\n    if not state:\n        return {\"ok\": False, \"error\": f\"任务不存在: {task_id}\"}\n\n    max_steps = 20\n    steps = 0\n\n    while steps < max_steps:\n        steps += 1\n        current = state[\"state\"]\n        handler = HANDLERS.get(current)\n\n        if not handler:\n            return {\"ok\": False, \"error\": f\"未知状态: {current}\"}\n\n        log.info(f\"[{task_id}] 执行: {current}\")\n        state = handler(state)\n\n        if state.get(\"_need_llm\"):\n            return {\n                \"ok\": True, \"paused\": True, \"reason\": \"need_llm\",\n                \"state\": state[\"state\"],\n                \"llm_context\": state.get(\"_llm_context\"),\n                \"task_id\": task_id,\n            }\n        if state.get(\"_need_user_input\"):\n            return {\n                \"ok\": True, \"paused\": True, \"reason\": \"need_user_input\",\n                \"state\": state[\"state\"],\n                \"prompt\": state.get(\"_prompt\"),\n                \"waiting_for\": state.get(\"_waiting_for\"),\n                \"task_id\": task_id,\n            }\n        if state.get(\"_completed\"):\n            return {\n                \"ok\": True, \"completed\": True,\n                \"failed\": state.get(\"_failed\", False),\n                \"summary\": state.get(\"_summary\"),\n                \"task_id\": task_id,\n            }\n\n    return {\"ok\": False, \"error\": \"超过最大步数限制\", \"task_id\": task_id}\n\n\ndef inject_data(task_id: str, data_key: str, data_value) -> dict:\n    state = load_state(task_id)\n    if not state:\n        return {\"ok\": False, \"error\": f\"任务不存在: {task_id}\"}\n\n    state[\"data\"][data_key] = data_value\n    save_state(task_id, state)\n    return {\"ok\": True, \"message\": f\"已注入: {data_key}\", \"task_id\": task_id}\n\n\ndef force_transition(task_id: str, new_state: str) -> dict:\n    state = load_state(task_id)\n    if not state:\n        return {\"ok\": False, \"error\": f\"任务不存在: {task_id}\"}\n    if new_state not in HANDLERS:\n        return {\"ok\": False, \"error\": f\"无效状态: {new_state}\"}\n    transition(state, new_state, \"forced_by_agent\")\n    return {\"ok\": True, \"message\": f\"已转移到: {new_state}\", \"task_id\": task_id}\n\n\n# ── CLI ───────────────────────────────────────────────\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    args = parse_args()\n    action = args.get(\"action\", \"status\")\n\n    if action == \"create\":\n        state = create_task(\n            company_id=args[\"company_id\"],\n            company_name=args[\"company_name\"],\n            period=args[\"period\"],\n            agg_org_id=str(args.get(\"agg_org_id\", args.get(\"aggOrgId\", \"\"))),\n            company_type=args.get(\"company_type\", \"small_scale\"),\n        )\n        output({\"ok\": True, \"task_id\": state[\"task_id\"], \"state\": state[\"state\"]})\n\n    elif action == \"advance\":\n        result = advance(args[\"task_id\"])\n        output(result)\n\n    elif action == \"status\":\n        state = load_state(args.get(\"task_id\", \"\"))\n        if state:\n            output({\n                \"ok\": True,\n                \"task_id\": state[\"task_id\"],\n                \"state\": state[\"state\"],\n                \"company_name\": state[\"company_name\"],\n                \"period\": state[\"period\"],\n                \"agg_org_id\": state.get(\"agg_org_id\"),\n                \"retry_count\": state[\"retry_count\"],\n                \"error\": state[\"error\"],\n                \"last_updated\": state[\"updated_at\"],\n            })\n        else:\n            output({\"ok\": False, \"error\": \"任务不存在\"})\n\n    elif action == \"inject\":\n        result = inject_data(args[\"task_id\"], args[\"data_key\"], args[\"data_value\"])\n        output(result)\n\n    elif action == \"force_transition\":\n        result = force_transition(args[\"task_id\"], args[\"new_state\"])\n        output(result)\n\n    elif action == \"list\":\n        tasks = list_tasks(args.get(\"status_filter\"))\n        output({\n            \"ok\": True,\n            \"tasks\": [{\n                \"task_id\": t[\"task_id\"],\n                \"company_name\": t[\"company_name\"],\n                \"period\": t[\"period\"],\n                \"state\": t[\"state\"],\n                \"agg_org_id\": t.get(\"agg_org_id\"),\n                \"updated_at\": t.get(\"updated_at\"),\n            } for t in tasks],\n            \"count\": len(tasks),\n        })\n\n    else:\n        output({\"ok\": False, \"error\": f\"未知 action: {action}\"})\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773821819802}}
{"type":"message","id":"5f66be43","parentId":"60242fe0","timestamp":"2026-03-18T08:17:19.447Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"现在我完全理解了流程。当前状态是 `CHECK_REQUIRED`，`proceed` 已经注入为 `true`。但根据状态机代码，`CHECK_REQUIRED` 在 advance 时会返回 `_need_llm`，然后需要通过 `handle_CHECK_REQUIRED_proceed` 来推进。\n\n让我检查状态机的 advance 逻辑 —— 当 advance 调用 `handle_CHECK_REQUIRED` 时，它会返回 `need_llm`，然后需要我处理这个 LLM 环节。既然用户已经注入了 `proceed: true`，我需要直接跳到 `DATA_INIT`。\n\n让我先执行 advance 看看返回什么，然后根据结果处理。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_9eff726ef47044f899ebd1cd","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/agents/qxy-declare/agent/tools && python3 state_machine.py '{\"action\":\"advance\", \"task_id\":\"decl_202602_test001\"}'"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":8045,"output":191,"cacheRead":19584,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":27820,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773821819806}}
