d_count\": 2,\n    \"message\": \"本月需申报 2 个税种，通知用户并开始流程\",\n    \"action\": \"告知用户本月需申报的税种清单，然后 inject data_key='proceed' data_value=true 继续\"\n  },\n  \"task_id\": \"decl_202602_test001\"\n}","cwd":"/Users/kristyzhang/.openclaw/workspace-qxy-declare"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773821839624}}
