{"type":"message","id":"3fe53c16","parentId":"e379fbe4","timestamp":"2026-03-18T08:18:09.752Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"**模拟测试公司（test001）2026年2月税务申报已成功完成！** ✅\n\n以下是完成摘要：\n\n| 项目 | 详情 |\n|------|------|\n| **企业名称** | 模拟测试公司 |\n| **企业ID** | test001 |\n| **申报期** | 2026-02 |\n| **申报状态** | **DONE（已完成）** |\n| **申报模式** | 零申报（应缴税额: ¥0.00） |\n\n**已完成的税种（2项）：**\n1. **增值税及附加税费（小规模纳税人）** — BDA0610606，征收期 2026-02-01 至 2026-02-28\n2. **企业所得税（季报）** — BDA0610100，征收期 2026-01-01 至 2026-03-31\n\n**流程推进记录：**\n- CHECK_REQUIRED → DATA_INIT（确认需申报2个税种，注入 proceed 推进）\n- DATA_INIT → WAIT_UPLOAD（两个税种初始化成功）\n- WAIT_UPLOAD → CONFIRM_INFO（注入零申报数据，跳过 Excel 上传）\n- CONFIRM_INFO → TAX_CALC（确认无无票收入）\n- TAX_CALC → SUBMIT（全零申报，走简易通道）\n- SUBMIT → DOWNLOAD → DONE（申报成功，回执已获取）\n\n**注意事项：**\n- 申报走的是企享云模拟环境（无 QXY_API_TOKEN 环境变量），接口返回 mock 数据\n- 回执 PDF URL: `https://mock.example.com/receipt.pdf`"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":2764,"output":343,"cacheRead":29540,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32647,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773821879580}}
